pr_body: New behavior: - `ply`: wrapped legacy custom reader. This is to handle the duplicated vertex issue by Assimp. - `stl`, `obj`, `off`, `gltf`, `glb`, `fbx`: ready by Assimp directly, not wrapped from legacy. Although they may still have the duplicated vertex issue, they match the behavior of the legacy code. This change is [](https://reviewable.io/reviews/isl-org/open3d/5415)
